{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/spring_data_jpa_@EntityGraph/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"MuSeong"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b24ba192-d591-574a-9b2d-396f0634a1b3","excerpt":"Fetch Join에 대한 포스팅\n링크 <>  @EntityGraph JPA의 Fetch Join을 Spring Data Jpa는 @EntityGraph로 해결 \n@EntityGraph(attributePaths = {\"연관 필드 명\"})  순수 JPA의 Fetch Join 예시 코드  Spring Data Jpa의 @EntityGraph를 이용한 Fet…","html":"<br>\n<p>Fetch Join에 대한 포스팅\n링크 &#x3C;></p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h1>@EntityGraph</h1>\n<p>JPA의 Fetch Join을 Spring Data Jpa는 @EntityGraph로 해결 <br>\n@EntityGraph(attributePaths = {\"연관 필드 명\"})</p>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>순수 JPA의 Fetch Join 예시 코드</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">String query = \"SELECT m from Member m join fetch m.team\";</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Spring Data Jpa의 @EntityGraph를 이용한 Fetch Join</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">@EntityGraph(attributePaths = {\"team\"})\nList&lt;Member> findMemberFetchJoin();</code></pre></div>\n<br>\n<br>\n<blockquote>\n<p>본 블로그는 인프런 '김영한'님의 강의를 정리한 내용입니다. 개인 공부 목적으로 작성된 글이며, 100% 정확한 내용이 아닐 수 있습니다.\n<br>출처  <a href=\"https://www.inflearn.com/course/%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0-JPA-%EC%8B%A4%EC%A0%84/dashboard\">https://www.inflearn.com/course/%EC%8A%A4%ED%94%84%EB%A7%81-%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%84%B0-JPA-%EC%8B%A4%EC%A0%84/dashboard</a></p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"Spring_Data_Jpa_Fetch Join","date":"September 23, 2023","update":"September 23, 2023","tags":["JPA","Spring Data Jpa"],"series":"Srping Data Jpa"},"fields":{"slug":"/spring_data_jpa_@EntityGraph/","readingTime":{"minutes":0.695}}},"seriesList":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"b24ba192-d591-574a-9b2d-396f0634a1b3","fields":{"slug":"/spring_data_jpa_@EntityGraph/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring_Data_Jpa_Fetch Join"}}},{"node":{"id":"e5b36dc0-5d29-5b34-bb01-88fe0bad3bc6","fields":{"slug":"/spring_data_jpa_1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring Data Jpa 1"}}},{"node":{"id":"56d69127-4ca5-53fb-92a9-436d93a90c9c","fields":{"slug":"/spring_data_jpa_페이징/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring_Data_Jpa_페이징, 정렬"}}},{"node":{"id":"4adbde27-5f9e-5a41-9e4a-6336c1de5956","fields":{"slug":"/spring_data_jpa_벌크성 쿼리/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring_Data_Jpa_벌크성 쿼리"}}},{"node":{"id":"a0bd26e6-6df8-5e8c-b7de-e6e5aaf16621","fields":{"slug":"/spring_data_jpa_Auditing/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring Data Jpa Auditing"}}},{"node":{"id":"381a7a88-ec5e-5f4a-8bae-bac85ee744b3","fields":{"slug":"/spring_data_jpa_사용자 정의 레파지토리/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring Data Jpa 사용자 정의 리파지토리"}}}]},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/jpql_JPQL 2편/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"JPQL 객체지향 쿼리 언어 2"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/spring_data_jpa_1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring Data Jpa 1"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"b24ba192-d591-574a-9b2d-396f0634a1b3","series":"Srping Data Jpa","previousPostId":"a89c017a-3541-5f7c-905b-6a3f18e17e2c","nextPostId":"e5b36dc0-5d29-5b34-bb01-88fe0bad3bc6"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}